#themuppetsmayhem

This press tour has been absolute MAYHEM!
(in the best way possible of course)

#themuppetsmayhem @themuppetsmayhem starts streaming MAY10th on @disneyplus

🌊🌊🌊

@themuppetsmayhem is coming to you May 10th on @disneyplus!!!!

🎸⚡️ @themuppetsmayhem IS STREAMING RIGHT NOW ON @disneyplus!!!! ✌🏽✨

All glory to God! To be able to get to do what I love for a living over and over again is truly a blessing! I’m just over here thankful lol

but back to the post … This photo was no joke taken on one of the best days of my life lol. I was so hype to do the scene where Lips & Animal use me as their pillow inside the mayhem van! And look how cute Animal looks when he’s sleeps! Don’t tell him I called him cute though - he hates that. 

But seriously - this show is so special to me. I’m so honored and humbled to be a part of it. The amount of sheer talent and artistry that I was surrounded by daily was incredible. We have the best crew in television! Them long hours created a family and I believe you’re going to feel that love when you watch it.  You also should know this is not a “kids” show - it’s a show FOR EVERYONE! And It’s got everything! Comedy! Drama! Muppets! Literal Cliffhangers! Even a crush that might possibly maybe lead to something bigger if only she could see me for who I really am, ya know?! Sorry - that was Moog taking over BUT speaking of Moog…

Moog. Is. Here!📍 I hope y’all ready to rock out with me and @electricmayhemband ! Get ready for a joy ride like no other! Buckle up and enjoy the mayhem!

All episodes of #TheMuppetsMayhem are now streaming on @DisneyPlus! @themuppetsmayhem

What a night! 🤘🏽⚡️♥️🎸✌🏽

Thank you @paulsmithdesign for the drip. 

All 10 episodes of @themuppetsmayhem are streaming right now on @disneyplus!

@26magazine 😎

“We first met Tahj Mowry in 1992 at just 5 years old debuting alongside greats like Patti Labelle & Vivica Fox!  If his industry origins were any indication, it’s no surprise that some 30 years later his face & name equity still stand strong, firmly legacied into the global, classic-entertainment landscape!  We caught up with the ‘Smart Guy’ ‘Baby Daddy’ actor chatting his definition of more life, allowing luxury & his huge NEW @disneyplus series @themuppetsmayhem !!”

“Outside of my cooking, I’m low-key a great barista [HA!] I pull off pretty good lattes & every now & then some equally as good latte art believe it or not! -Catch me on the right day & you might end up with a pretty convincing swan!  Also, fun fact: I keep to-go coffee cups at my house, so if friends & family come over & they want a specialized cup of coffee, I can make them a ‘Tahj’ latte, complete with to-go cup for my guest on the move!”

“Today is all I have, so what can I do to be an example to the people around me today? What can I do to have more peace & more joy today, -let me go do those things! Just having that mindset of ‘hey, today is the only day I have, let me stay in the present, let me be present in these great experiences that I'm having right now & not stress about things of tomorrow or things that I can't control’. More life is here, more life is now”.

My main goal in this new year is to allow God to rule more and more in every area of my life and more specifically, in all the little moments that lead up to the big ones.

I want to wake up each day committed to live in those small moments with open eyes and a humble and expectant heart. 

“God’s work in you is a process, not an event. It progresses not in three or four huge moments, but in ten thousand little moments of change.”
- New Morning Mercies by Paul David Tripp 

Let’s live by faith, in hope and in love. 
Happy New Year ♥️
